Welcome to EditPy.


Generic:
           esc: enter/exit command mode
       up/down: scroll up/down
    left/right: move caret left/right
     ctrl+left: increase selection to left
    ctrl+right: increase selection to right

Command Mode:
         enter: input command
             a: select all
    h[<t>]/<r>: replace regex <r> with forward-slash-less text <t>
     n[<path>]: create and open new file, with optional path
     o[<path>]: open <path> or empty file
             p: print current file
             q: quit editor
     s[<path>]: save or save to <path>
             w: close file
             ?: opens help
      =[index]: moves caret to <index>

Shortcuts:
        ctrl+a: select all
        ctrl+c: copy text
        ctrl+q: quit editor
        ctrl+n: create file
        ctrl+o: open file
        ctrl+s: save file
        ctrl+v: paste text
        ctrl+w: close file
        ctrl+/: open help

Dialogs:
           esc: cancel action
         enter: confirm input
    arrow keys: move caret/select option
